Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:55.76,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2\fnFOT-PalRamune Std B\fs58\pos(736,3)}彿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:04.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}此刻便已如注定  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:10.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}風兒歌唱  雨滴訴説
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:15.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我們終將抵達  那光之居所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:19.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}層層　　  交織重重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:19.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2\fnFOT-PalRamune Std B\fs54\pos(585,5)}疊疊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:23.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}是地球上巧妙的偶然
